            "chunk_index": 1,
            "text": "116 OG No. 35, 5411 (August 31, 2020)\n\n[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 11484, August 14, 2020 ]\n\nAN ACT CONVERTING THE ROAD STRETCHING FROM BARANGAY ANDUYAN, MUNICIPALITY OF TUBAO, PROVINCE OF LA UNION TO BARANGAY SAN PASCUAL, MUNICIPALITY OF TUBA, PROVINCE OF BENGUET INTO A NATIONAL ROAD ANS APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR\n\nBe it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:\n\nSECTION 1. The road stretching from Barangay Anduyan, Municipality of Tubao, Province of La Union to Barangay San Pascual, Municipality of Tuba, Province of Benguet as described in the technical description under the succeeding section of this Act is hereby converted into a national road.",
